# Auto-Beratung Website

One-page car consulting website with AI-powered vehicle lookup tool. Built for a TikTok creator who offers personalized car recommendations for 49€.

## What This Project Is

A single-page German-language website where users can:
1. Enter a car model and get detailed specs, known defects, and depreciation data (AI-powered)
2. Buy a 49€ car consultation product via Stripe Checkout
3. Fill out a form with their car preferences during checkout
4. The site owner receives the customer's data via email and responds within 48 hours with 3 car suggestions

**All user-facing text MUST be in German (Deutsch).**

