## 49€ Product & Stripe Checkout

### Purchase Flow
1. User fills out the form fields (see below)
2. User clicks "49€ bezahlen und Beratung anfragen"
3. Stripe Checkout session is created (server-side)
4. User is redirected to Stripe Checkout (hosted by Stripe, PCI-compliant)
5. After successful payment:
   - Site owner receives an email with all customer data + form responses
   - Customer sees a confirmation page ("Vielen Dank! Du erhältst innerhalb von 48 Stunden 3 Auto-Vorschläge per E-Mail")
6. Stripe webhook confirms payment on the server

### Form Fields (all labels in German)
- "Dein Budget (€)" — number input
- "Gewünschte Automarke" — text input
- "Bevorzugter Karosserietyp" — select (Kleinwagen, Limousine, SUV, Kombi, Coupé, Cabrio, Van)
- "Getriebe-Präferenz" — radio (Schaltgetriebe, Automatik, egal)
- "Antrieb" — radio (Frontantrieb, Heckantrieb, Allrad, egal)
- "Weitere Wünsche / Anmerkungen" — textarea
- "Deine E-Mail-Adresse" — email input (required)

These fields must be submitted **before or during** the Stripe Checkout — either as part of the checkout form or as a pre-checkout step that gets attached to the order via metadata.

